writers with a safe place to
create art and build community.

51:50.407 --> 51:54.678 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CORNELIUS EADY, Co-Founder, Cave
Canem: Validation is really one
of things that's so incredibly

51:54.678 --> 52:01.118 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
