52:05.956 --> 52:14.164 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BILL MURRAY: I think it just
gives me an opportunity to, you
know, hear some sort of voice of
the

52:14.164 --> 52:18.669 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
